LOCUS       186_attP                 307 bp    DNA              UNK 01-JAN-1980
DEFINITION  Bacteriophage 186 attP site-specific recombination attachment site
            (NC_001317.1 20867-21173) — Int arm/core sites, one P-arm IHF site,
            the tRNA-Ile/attB core with 7-bp crossover, and five Apl excisionase
            operators..
